# Movie Organizer - Git Attributes
# Author: Pablo Murad (runawaydevil)
# Repository: https://github.com/runawaydevil/organizer-movies.git

# ===========================================
# Text Files
# ===========================================
*.py text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.txt text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.spec text eol=lf

# ===========================================
# Binary Files
# ===========================================
*.exe binary
*.ico binary
*.jpg binary
*.png binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary

# ===========================================
# Documentation
# ===========================================
README.md linguist-documentation
API_SETUP.md linguist-documentation
CLI_USAGE.md linguist-documentation
CONTRIBUTING.md linguist-documentation
CHANGELOG.md linguist-documentation
LICENSE linguist-documentation

# ===========================================
# Generated Files (should be ignored)
# ===========================================
*.pyc linguist-generated
*.pyo linguist-generated
__pycache__/ linguist-vendored
build/ linguist-vendored
dist/ linguist-vendored
release/ linguist-vendored

# ===========================================
# Configuration Examples
# ===========================================
*.example.json linguist-documentation
